reviews.text: Cozy enviroment, normal price of food
Very nice place and the steak is fine enough
Food was acceptable.  A bit over priced for this level of quality, but good selection at the buffet area.
Good food and decent place for chatting

I'd have very much liked to give this a higher rating.  I'll first talk about breakfast at Pentalounge, which I must say is quite lovely. It has plenty of variety, its quiet, and the price is very reasonable.

The same cannot be said for their dinner however.  While the prices are still fair, the quality of food takes a dramatic fall.  Ive had both fish and chips, as well as I believe a fillet of ribeye.

While the beef was for the most part alright if a little overcooked, the fish was absolutely disappointing.  It arrived at the table a lovely golden brown with a light batter which i must say was very inviting, however the fish was massacred. It did not flake as a white fish should and unfortunately the batter didnt stick as it should.  Id have to equate it to a plate full of mush.  

That said the chips were spot on, and the Pentabeer offered here is quite refreshing. 

The servers are rather friendly, and the atmosphere is quite nice, and its a real shame the dinner doesnt match the rest of the positives.

result.name: Pentahotel Hong Kong, Tuen Mun

reviews.text: Stylish design, airy space, good adjustable ac. Convenient location close to tuen mun MTR and bus/light rail terminals

Good service
Comfortable
worth to pay
Near the mal and MRT

Great hotel! Clean very friendly staff who can actually speak good English!!! The room was huge compared to other hotels I've stayed at the staff are polite and willing to help! It's in a great location close to Vcity shopping mall very convenient and would highly recommend to anyone coming to this area. I will definitely book this hotel when coming back to this area in Hong Kong

The hotel is very close to the MTR station and the view from our room was absolutely fantastic. There is also a nice restaurant in the hotel although the service was rather tardy and at some point no one was actually available to serve us even when it was not crowded. Before the trip we have also emailed Pentahotel regarding the late check out and they replied to us promptly. They also agreed to our request for a further extension on the check out day as our event ended slightly later than expected. We were quite disappointed because of the payment issue we have faced prior to our stay. The hotel attempted to process our payment on the day before our stay. Unfortunately, because of the difference between the main guest's name and credit card payer's name, they were unable to process and required us to pay the hotel in cash upon our arrival. We found this ridiculous because there would definitely be instances where hotel bookings are made under a different credit card payer (such as booking for our family or friends). The hotel should look into their payment policy.
Friendly staff and helpful. Excellent Location close to shops, Mass Transit Rail, Bus terminal and restaurant all.

result.name: 屯門貝爾特酒店

reviews.text: 在市中心方便交通多大形商場及在警署邊出入安全安心
酒店風枱有特色，但房入面6個usb頭都係壞既，個冷氣仲要成日發出嘈音…

在check in 時自動upgrade 我家庭房令我高興。家庭房算寛敞，房間整潔，浴巾也乾浄。但淋浴間的門有不足，水由旁邊流出門外，令浴室地面有大量水。
另check out 時也要等候十幾分中，但OK後無通知我，要我主動查詢才吿知我可以了。此点比較疏忽。
整体来説酒店內環境也算不錯！
住10樓 但冷氣不涼，房間濕氣超重，被子都濕濕的，但服務人員態度很好。
